Package: lineartestr
Type: Package
Title: Linear Specification Testing with Estimated Variables
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Federico", "Garza", , "fede.garza.ramirez@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7015-8186"))
Maintainer: Federico Garza <fede.garza.ramirez@gmail.com>
Description: Tests if the linear hypothesis of a model
    is correct specified, using reset and Dominguez Lobato tests.
